---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

import TrelloWidget from "../components/TrelloWidget.astro";
import TrelloSuggestion from "../components/TrelloSuggestion.astro";
import FeaturedPostsWidget from "../components/FeaturedPostsWidget.astro";

const pageTitle = "Home"
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
	<br>
	<p>
		Welcome to my devlog for my game development side project! I'm documenting what I'm learning and experimenting with for education and fun.
	</p>
	<p>
		I put together this site using the 
		<a class="accent-link" href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro.js</a> 
		framework and styled it with
		<a class="accent-link" href="https://tailwindcss.com/" target="_blank">Tailwind</a>. 
		Check out the code on 
		<a class="accent-link" href="https://github.com/c-lonas/astro-timeless-devlog" target="_blank"> GitHub</a> 
		to see how it comes together!
	</p>

	<br>
	<p>
		This is a read-only view of a trello board I created to track progress on the project, displayed here via the Trello API.
	</p>
	<p>
		You can use the green button below to add a card to the board in the suggestion column.
	</p>

